data.text:
Justin Moore is booked for a EPIC show Saturday August 11th. Making the first country artist appearance at the MEC. Tickets are ON SALE NOW!!! We promised to take entertainment to the next level with our brand new facility and we are delivering. Join the event on facebook for giveaways, event details and other cool stuff.

Buy tickets online here or Call the box office at 260-768-4990 to buy via phone

Arkansas native JUSTIN MOORE spent three years putting together his fourth studio album, KINDA DON’T CARE. The project is chock-full of new music and earned the singer his third consecutive No. 1 album debut. The platinum-selling entertainer kickstarted the album with his sixth chart-topping single “You Look Like I Need A Drink” and follow-up single “Somebody Else Will.” A known road warrior, Moore has shared the stage stage with Hank Williams Jr., Brad Paisley, Miranda Lambert and Brantley Gilbert and is currently on his headlining AMERICAN MADE TOUR with Lee Brice.
